Now let's go ahead and label the hair layer and we'll just call it hair next.

10:03.870 --> 10:10.730
Let's create those goggles so we're going to turn off our hair layer and our head layer so we can see

10:10.730 --> 10:12.360
the goggles on the sketch.

10:13.160 --> 10:20.250
And let's add a new layer and using the Lasso tool once again we're going to trace out that shape.

